(Only list software related info)

A. Correctness of Hardware Setup
       - Upgrade the system BISO to the latest stable version.
B. Upgrade Software Component
       - Linux OS distribution version
       - Hadoop distribution version
       - JDK version
       - Other third-party libraries that the Hadoop framework depends on
C. Performing Stress Tests
       - Hadoop micro-benchmarks (DFSIO, NNBemch, MRBench): used to stress test the setup of Hadoop framework


